---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/mainLayout.astro';
import { getLangFromUrl, useTranslatedPath } from '../i18n/utils.ts';

const lang = getLangFromUrl(Astro.url);
const translatePath = useTranslatedPath(lang);
---

<MainLayout lang="sr" title="Magnet And Care">
	<section class="relative flex justify-center py-8 sm:py-24 lg:bg-[url('/hand-hero.jpg')] bg-cover bg-fixed bg-no-repeat bg-secondary/30">
		<div class="relative z-10 mx-4 sm:mx-20 2xl:mx-0 2xl:w-4/5 flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-5 lg:gap-16 xl:gap-5 2xl:gap-0">
			<div class="lg:w-2/3 2xl:w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-4 order-1 lg:order-none">
				<div class="mb-2 md:mb-0 2xl:mb-2 font-bold text-xl sm:text-3xl xl:text-4xl sm:text-nowrap text-center lg:text-start">Dobrodošli u <h1 class="gradient-text inline-block">Magnet And Care</h1> DOO</div>
				<p class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-center sm:text-justify lg:text-start">
					Naša misija je pružanje vrhunskih usluga u različitim sektorima, uključujući negu starijih i invalidnih osoba, usluge u hotelijerstvu i ugostiteljstvu, kao i održavanje radne čistoće u komunalnim preduzećima. Sa sedištem u Apatinu, Srbija, naš stručni tim posvećen je svakodnevnom unapređenju kvaliteta života i rada svih korisnika naših usluga. Sa pažnjom i profesionalnošću, pružamo podršku svima kojima su naše usluge potrebne.
				</p>
				<div class="w-max flex flex-col sm:flex-row self-center lg:self-start items-center gap-5 sm:gap-10 lg:gap-5 text-center lg:text-start">
					<a href={translatePath('/about/')} class="inline-block max-w-max px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-center bg-accent font-bold text-lg">Saznajte više o nama</a>
					<a href={translatePath('/contact/')} class="inline-block max-w-max px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-center bg-primary md:hover:bg-accent duration-300 font-bold text-lg text-background md:hover:text-text">Kontaktirajte nas</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="flex justify-center grow order-0 lg:order-none">
				<img src="/mc-logo.svg" alt="Logo" class="w-24 sm:w-48 xl:w-72">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="absolute z-0 top-0 left0 w-full h-full lg:bg-white/80"></div>
	</section>
	<section class="flex justify-center">
		<div class="sm:w-4/5 mt-24 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-16 text-lg">
			<div class="relative w-320 h-360 p-8 flex flex-col flex-nowrap justify-center border-4 border-accent rounded-lg">
				<h2 class="absolute -top-6 -left-1 py-1 pr-2 bg-background font-bold text-2xl">Radno vreme</h2>
				<ul class="flex flex-col gap-3.5">
					<li class="flex justify-between">
						<span>Ponedeljak</span>
						<span>08:30 - 16:30</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex justify-between">
						<span>Utorak</span>
						<span>08:30 - 16:30</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex justify-between">
						<span>Sreda</span>
						<span>08:30 - 16:30</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex justify-between">
						<span>Četvrtak</span>
						<span>08:30 - 16:30</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex justify-between">
						<span>Petak</span>
						<span>08:30 - 16:30</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex justify-between">
						<span>Subota</span>
						<span class="text-red-600">ZATVORENO</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex justify-between">
						<span>Nedelja</span>
						<span class="text-red-600">ZATVORENO</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="relative w-320 h-360 p-8 flex flex-col flex-nowrap justify-center border-4 border-accent rounded-lg">
				<h2 class="absolute -top-6 -left-1 py-1 pr-2 bg-background font-bold text-2xl">Hitni kontakt</h2>
				<div class="h-full flex flex-col justify-around">
					<a href="tel:+381641188942" class="min-w-max p-4 flex justify-around gap-2 flex-nowrap bg-accent md:hover:bg-primary md:hover:text-background duration-300 rounded-full text-center">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-6 fill-text"><title>phone-alert</title><path d="M6.62,10.79C8.06,13.62 10.38,15.94 13.21,17.38L15.41,15.18C15.69,14.9 16.08,14.82 16.43,14.93C17.55,15.3 18.75,15.5 20,15.5A1,1 0 0,1 21,16.5V20A1,1 0 0,1 20,21A17,17 0 0,1 3,4C3,3.44 3.45,3 4,3H7.5A1,1 0 0,1 8.5,4C8.5,5.24 8.7,6.45 9.07,7.57C9.18,7.92 9.1,8.31 8.82,8.58L6.62,10.79M17,12V10H19V12H17M17,8V2H19V8H17Z" /></svg>
						<div class="font-semibold text-xl">+381-64-1188942</div>
					</a>
					<p>
						Za hitan kontakt pozovite nas, i neko iz našeg tima će vam odgovoriti u najkraćem roku tokom radnog vremena. <span class="font-semibold">Vaša briga je naš prioritet.</span>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="relative w-320 h-360 p-8 flex flex-col flex-nowrap justify-center border-4 border-accent rounded-lg">
				<h2 class="absolute -top-6 -left-1 py-1 pr-2 bg-background font-bold text-2xl">Pružamo vam</h2>
				<div class="h-full flex flex-col gap-5">
					<ul class="h-full flex flex-col flex-nowrap justify-between">
						<ul>
							<h3 class="text-xl mb-1 font-semibold">Naše usluge</h3>
							<p>
								Podrška u svakom trenutku.
							</p>
							<a href={translatePath('/service/')} class="inline-block max-w-max mt-0.5 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-center font-bold text-lg bg-accent md:hover:bg-primary md:hover:text-background duration-300">Saznaj više</a>
						</ul>
						<ul>
							<h3 class="text-xl mb-1 font-semibold">Vaš posao</h3>
							<p>
								Prilike koje menjaju život na bolje.
							</p>
							<a href={translatePath('/career/')} class="inline-block max-w-max mt-0.5 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-center font-bold text-lg bg-accent md:hover:bg-primary md:hover:text-background duration-300">Saznaj više</a>
						</ul>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
	
.gradient-text {
	background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(13, 124, 131), rgb(95, 221, 230));
	-webkit-background-clip: text;
	-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
	background-clip: text;
	text-fill-color: transparent;
}

</style>